---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="About — Global Faith Temple"
  description="The mission, vision, goals, and guiding principles of Global Faith Temple — a sanctuary built in gratitude to all who served in Vietnam."
>
  <main>
    <!-- Page header -->
    <header class="relative bg-ivory pb-16 pt-40 md:pb-24 md:pt-48">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
        <p class="fade-up mb-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-olive opacity-80">About</p>
        <h1 class="fade-up font-serif text-4xl leading-[1.1] text-olive-deep md:text-6xl">
          A quiet place,<br />an open door.
        </h1>
        <p class="fade-up mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.78);">
          Global Faith Temple is a sanctuary built in gratitude — for the soldiers of the Republic of Vietnam, the
          United States, and the six allied nations who answered the same call. These are the convictions that shape
          our work, day by quiet day.
        </p>
        <div class="fade-up mt-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-olive opacity-50">
          <span class="h-px w-10" style="background: rgba(74,76,33,0.4);"></span>
          <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10"><circle cx="5" cy="5" r="1.4" fill="currentColor"></circle></svg>
          <span class="h-px w-10" style="background: rgba(74,76,33,0.4);"></span>
        </div>
        <nav class="fade-up mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-olive opacity-70">
          <a href="#mission" class="hover:text-olive">Mission</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#vision" class="hover:text-olive">Vision</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#goals" class="hover:text-olive">Goals</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#principles" class="hover:text-olive">Principles</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <section id="mission" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Our mission</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">To hold space for peace — steadily, faithfully, for as long as we are able.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed md:col-span-8" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
          <p>
            Global Faith Temple exists to gather people in worship and reflection, to honor every soldier who served in
            Vietnam, and to extend quiet care to the families and comrades who carry their memory.
          </p>
          <p>
            We do not measure our work in numbers, but in moments — a candle lit before dawn, a name spoken aloud, a
            stranger received as a friend, a grief held without hurry.
          </p>
          <p class="font-serif italic text-olive">
            "Peace is the slow work of many hands. We are honored to lend ours."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Vision -->
    <section id="vision" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1); background-color: var(--parchment);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Our vision</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">A community in which remembrance becomes a way of life.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed md:col-span-8" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
          <p>
            We imagine a world where the memory of those who fell — and the gratitude owed to those who returned — is
            not pushed aside by the noise of ordinary days, but woven gently into them: in our meals, our greetings, our
            shared silences, our care for the elders among us.
          </p>
          <p>
            A temple without walls, present wherever people gather to honor what was given, and to tend what was
            preserved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Goals -->
    <section id="goals" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Our goals</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">Small, durable commitments we renew each year.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8">
          <ul class="stagger space-y-4">
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-32 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">Sanctuary</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">Keep our doors open daily — freely, without ticket, without expectation. Every visitor is a guest.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-32 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">Remembrance</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">Honor the soldiers of Vietnam and her allies — in word, in daily ceremony, and in care for the families they left behind.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-32 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">Community</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">Cultivate gatherings — shared meals, study circles, seasonal observances — that knit neighbors into something larger than themselves.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-32 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">Service</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">Walk alongside veterans, their widows, their elders, and any soul quietly burdened by what war has cost them.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-32 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">Stewardship</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">Carry our founder's gift with humility — preserving every brick, every record, every name — and entrust the temple well to those who follow.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Principles -->
    <section id="principles" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1); background-color: var(--beige);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Our principles</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">Convictions we return to, again and again.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8">
          <div class="stagger grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Peace before persuasion</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">We meet each person as they are. We do not press, we do not corner, we do not require agreement.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Remembrance over forgetting</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">We name what was lost. We honor what was given. We refuse the easy comfort of forgetting.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Service in quiet</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Our work is done without spectacle. Faithfulness, repeated daily, is its own witness.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Hospitality without test</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">No creed is asked at the threshold. Only an invitation to sit, to rest, to be at home.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Gratitude as practice</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">We notice the gift in ordinary days. We give thanks aloud, often, and without embarrassment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Care across borders</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Our circle of concern reaches Vietnam, the United States, Korea, Australia, New Zealand, Thailand, the Philippines, and the Republic of China — and beyond.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
